Ginkgo, Vitamin E, and Reishi [1("https://magicscoop.com/blogs/inside-scoop/reishi-simplified-mushroom-supports-immunity-stress?srsltid=AfmBOoqILex-qC7xSqWddSHEfnl6IT_Z6Eut9LF81Cqoo3wIonoI-Fm3")]\
