\f2 \uc0\u9888 \u65039 
\f0  The Oxidation Paradox: Chlorine Dioxide vs. Mushrooms\
\
The Conflict: \
\
Medicinal mushrooms rely on their delicate polysaccharide and triterpene structures to activate your immune system. Chlorine Dioxide (ClO\uc0\u8322 ) is a powerful, unselective oxidant that will immediately break down and neutralize these organic structures if they come into direct contact. [1, 2("https://balancecoffee.co.uk/blogs/blog/who-should-not-drink-mushroom-coffee?srsltid=AfmBOoqtE-d4701gqXvXsBr-4nUQMyZjXYbhjPaiO0rxvIIRRTB61x8I")]\
\
The Safety Adjustment: \
